---
title: One-Pot Ravioli Bake with Spinach, Thyme, and Parmesan Breadcrumbs
description: Just when we thought pasta night couldn’t get any better, our chefs doubled down on the spinach. This nutritious green can be found in the ravioli AND fresh in the gratin. But we have a feeling your kids will be too busy devouring the panko breadcrumbs and creamy Parmesan to notice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mushroom-ravioli-gratin-w48-fab778b2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mushroom-ravioli-gratin-w48-606d54c6.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/mushroom-ravioli-gratin-w48-581222a8c7262876ca1aab02
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 445 kcal
